User Stories

When I open the page I want to have multiple options for products to start with

I want to be able to close the page and reopen at the same spot

I want to be able name my product manufacturing company.

I want to be able to affect the success of my company's production line.

I want a simple, rich, and interactive UI experience.

I want to push buttons that do things and see the results.

I want an approachable and modern 2d graphic art style.

I want to learn about interesting science and manufacturing processes.

Interactions should be intuitive and easy to understand. The site should guide the player.

I want the site to be mobile friendly

